      "rationale": "Three mesh densities evaluated (coarse ~85k elements, medium ~220k, fine ~510k). QoI (force at 40 mm) changed 0.9% from medium to fine. GCI computed as 1.8%. Achieved level 3 exceeds required level 2, providing additional margin."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical solver error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative solver residuals below 1e-6; energy balance error below 0.1% for all load steps.",
      "rationale": "Nonlinear quasi-static analyses used Newton-Raphson iteration with force residual tolerance 1e-7. Energy balance error across all 11 replicate simulations ranged 0.003–0.041%. No divergence events recorded. Achieved level equals required level."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Use error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent review of model setup by second analyst; documented checklist of boundary condition, material assignment, and loading inputs.",
