      "rationale": "The validation activity is identical to the COU scenario: ASTM F1717 static compression-bending of the non-cannulated 7.5 mm construct. No scenario extrapolation is required. The FEA model is applied in validation mode under conditions that are indistinguishable from the intended regulatory use. This represents the highest achievable relevance for this factor."
    }
